The People

Meet the Team

Est.
2026

Valotac is an independent VR studio built for the next generation of players. We make consumer-first games — wacky, scary, fun — designed to pull Gen Z and Gen Alpha into worlds they actually want to be in.

Our focus is on immersive experiences that tap into the trends, humour, and interests of our generation. VR isn't just a platform to us, it's the medium through which we can improve how we communicate and socialise together.
